{"tid":1931542,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國際特赦組織斥外交部針對傳媒言論自由攻擊可恥","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T08:33:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40d636e8b18299245dd6336687157b60c3945d83","tid":1931542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"外交部要求《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》和《華盛頓郵報》年底前記者證到期的美籍記者，10日內交還記者證，今後不得在內地包括港澳從事記者工作。國際特赦組織認為，外交部針對傳媒言論自由的攻擊可恥。<br />\n<br />\n組織表示，這些記者揭示當局無數遍佈新疆至香港侵犯人權的行為，亦有深入調查武漢的新型肺炎疫情，中美針鋒相對、以牙還牙，在全球需要攜手對抗疫情時禁止傳媒採訪，將為中國甚至全球的公共衞生帶來重大惡果。<br />\n<br />\n組織又表示，事件再次反映出在所謂自治和一國兩制下，港澳兩地的自由不斷被嚴重磨蝕，情況令人擔憂，特區政府必須立即澄清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515271-20200318.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515271-20200318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=68f7b0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515271-20200318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d11a24b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515271-20200318.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ee2676660dfc2a791f7b1e45fdabf65f2014bba2","tid":1931542,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122630de04898adc01a34222916afeb86645fa22","tid":1931542,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑話：HK有言論自由"},{"pid":"cd3a348fe8dd7dcd56165f95eb6daf97e09f5056","tid":1931542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T